{
  "stem": "20088.9",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was convinced my father would turn up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And each time I heard a taxi pull up outside, I rushed to the window and thought, well, my father was here.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it, of course, never happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I worked very hard at school, and I became a very good pupil, in comparison to that I was very bad before.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I quite enjoyed learning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Running But as I said, I wasn't happy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the children felt that I was miserable, and they made me head girl, which I did, but again, not-- my heart wasn't in.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, when I had two more years to go-- I don't actually know why, because we were not that poor-- but my mother said, it's better that you learn already a profession, so that when you finish school, that you can earn money.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't really know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't want to learn anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't want to be anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother said, you're a bit arty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think you should be a photographer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I didn't particularly want to be a photographer, but I didn't know anything else, and I was a very obedient child.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, oh, all right, I'll be a photographer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so we knew somebody in town who had a studio, and they were doing art photography.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And for-- they made slides for courses which was used in history at art.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Let's say they were doing Michelangelo, so we went to the museum to take all the picture which the professor was going to use then later.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's where I learned taking photos and printing and-- and everything,",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] but I had to do is this together with school.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
